  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The Miracle Hometel also offers meeting and banquet facilities. Recreational facilities like gymnasium, sauna, steam room, spa and swimming pool are also available.  (06/08SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Just about 6 kilometers away from Suvarnabhumi Airport. Hotel also provides complimentary transfer from and to hotel to airport, but the flight detail is a must to provide for picking up.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Hotel features 85 rooms in total, well mixed with deluxe, junior suites and miracle suites. Deluxe room is medium size with 32 square meters on carpet floor. Room is without balcony but decorated stylish which are equipped with all the essential facilities like safety box, mini bar. Bathroom is good with separate bathtub and shower.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>A low-rise building constructed with concrete and glass.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The coffee shop offers sumptuous Chinese and Japanese cuisine for all day dinning. The in-house bar, which is also an ideal place to relax.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
